{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"887f6iu9h2cv2z63od6hzis","title":"しりとりでアイデアを作る","desc":"","updated":1649652168078,"created":1649650654649,"custom":{},"fname":"reference.brainstorming-methods.word-chain-refinement.ja","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","name":"digital-garden","selfContained":true},"contentHash":"8b4f39a0899fd1bd5105203f7fe38215","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"reference.brainstorming-methods.word-chain-refinement.ja","id":"887f6iu9h2cv2z63od6hzis","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"reference.brainstorming-methods.word-chain-refinement","alias":"english","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":17},"end":{"line":4,"column":66,"offset":82},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"reference.brainstorming-methods.word-chain-refinement"}},{"from":{"fname":"reference.brainstorming-methods.word-chain-refinement","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":26},"end":{"line":4,"column":70,"offset":95},"indent":[]},"value":"reference.brainstorming-methods.word-chain-refinement.ja","alias":"Japanese"}],"anchors":{"しりとりでアイデアを作る":{"type":"header","text":"しりとりでアイデアを作る","value":"しりとりでアイデアを作る","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"step-1-5-min":{"type":"header","text":"Step 1 (5 min)","value":"step-1-5-min","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"step2-20min":{"type":"header","text":"Step2 (20min)","value":"step2-20min","line":24,"column":0,"depth":2},"wait-5-min":{"type":"header","text":"Wait (5 min)","value":"wait-5-min","line":38,"column":0,"depth":2},"step-3-10-min":{"type":"header","text":"Step 3 (10 min)","value":"step-3-10-min","line":41,"column":0,"depth":2},"step-4":{"type":"header","text":"Step 4","value":"step-4","line":52,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"c74f8fvcyklc23u3056l529","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"しりとりでアイデアを作る\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#しりとりでアイデアを作る\"></a>しりとりでアイデアを作る</h1>\n<p><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/c74f8fvcyklc23u3056l529\">english</a></p>\n<p>（<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/react-sports-2022/\">Reactアプリコンテスト\n「#ウンドウノキッカケ」</a> で見た。）</p>\n<h2 id=\"step-1-5-min\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#step-1-5-min\"></a>Step 1 (5 min)</h2>\n<p>自由にしりとりをしてください。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>なるべくベタなワードは書かない（「りんご」、「ごりら」、「らっぱ」など）</li>\n<li>「ん」で終わってもＯＫ！「ん」の1文字前から続ける（「みかん」→「かんずめ」）</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>No</th><th>しりとり</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"step2-20min\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#step2-20min\"></a>Step2 (20min)</h2>\n<p>アイデア創造</p>\n<ul>\n<li>テーマ×ワードで思いつくアイデアを２つ書く（あれば３つ以上OK）</li>\n<li>テーマやワードからちょっとズレてるかな？など気にしない</li>\n<li>とにかく数を出す</li>\n<li>突飛なアイデア歓迎</li>\n<li>20～30秒考えて思いつかなければパスしてOK</li>\n<li>頭をフル回転させてください</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>No</th><th>テーマ</th><th>ワード</th><th>アイデア</th><th>アイデア2</th><th>アイデア3（あれば)</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"wait-5-min\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#wait-5-min\"></a>Wait (5 min)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>おつかれさまです、5分間休憩してください。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"step-3-10-min\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#step-3-10-min\"></a>Step 3 (10 min)</h2>\n<p>アイデア選定</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Step2で作ったアイデアの中から使えそうなものを出す</li>\n<li>Step2を見直して、良さそうなのは背景色変えるとかするとわかりやすいかも</li>\n<li>事前に考えてきたアイデアもここに書く</li>\n<li>Step2で書いたものをさらにブラッシュアップも可</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>No</th><th>アイデア</th><th>説明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"step-4\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#step-4\"></a>Step 4</h2>\n<p>発表</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1人1分で発表いただきます。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/c74f8fvcyklc23u3056l529\">Word Chain Refinement</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","title":"Home","desc":"","updated":1655543408062,"created":1648806032875,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","name":"digital-garden","selfContained":true},"contentHash":"85274ee61d0bc9adc52197cbfa78a37d","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"contact_me","alias":"contact_me","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":55,"offset":331},"end":{"line":10,"column":69,"offset":345},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"contact_me"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"areas.gamedev","alias":"areas.gamedev","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":3,"offset":389},"end":{"line":14,"column":20,"offset":406},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"areas.gamedev"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"areas.software-development","alias":"areas.software-development","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":3,"offset":409},"end":{"line":15,"column":33,"offset":439},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"areas.software-development"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"reference.faith-and-work","alias":"reference.faith-and-work","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":3,"offset":442},"end":{"line":16,"column":31,"offset":470},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"reference.faith-and-work"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"reference.spiritual-abuse","alias":"reference.spiritual-abuse","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":3,"offset":480},"end":{"line":18,"column":32,"offset":5